    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly so sad to let this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for a new home! This car is in absolutely pristine, mint condition\u2014it seriously looks and drives like it just rolled off the showroom floor. I\u2019ve babied it since day one, and it really shows! If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s basically perfect without the brand-new price tag, you\u2019ve totally found it. Come take a look and see for yourself, you\u2019re going to love it!",
      "price": 43500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
